s for the related processes to do\ninternal work. Technically, this is defined as a `Bisimulation` on the saturation of the LTS. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Bisimulation.html#Cslib.LTS.IsWeakBisimulation","kind":"def","line":786,"name":"Cslib.LTS.IsWeakBisimulation","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/7f88669e78c0fa9d9c4f41a397072114cbb9aa7e/Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Bisimulation.lean#L786-L790"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Bisimulation.html#Cslib.Bisimilarity.symm_simulation\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">Bisimilarity</span>.<span class=\"name\">symm_simulation</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">State</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Label</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">lts</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Basic.html#Cslib.LTS\">LTS</a> <span class=\"fn\">State</span> <span class=\"fn\">Label</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/LTS/Bisimulation.html#Cslib.Bisimilarity\">Bisimilarity</a> <span class=\"fn\">lts</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">s1</span> <span class=\"fn\">s2</span> : <span class=\"fn\">State</span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">State</span> → <span class=\"fn\">State</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_typ